# IMPORTANT: do NOT ignore /public/data or /public/papers here.
# The repo's .gitignore excludes them (they are regenerated by the
# precompute pipeline), but Vercel must upload them as static assets.
# When .vercelignore is missing, Vercel falls back to .gitignore, which
# is why an earlier deploy went out with empty panels.
